name: Bitsune Miku - Crypto Guardian
description: "As long  as we HODL, the grass is always greener on our side."  -Bitsune Miku  The OG Crypto Guardian    This is an 8 bit rendering of Bitsune Miku.  Crypto Guardian Collection: In honor to the top 25 market cap coins, Guardians have arrived to protect the hashes of all blockchains . Each guardian gathers the essence of the coin it represents. Bitsune is the first of these art pieces. (1/25)    About the artist: I am a female Artrepreneur with a Bachelor Degree in Arts. I lost my normie 9 to 5 job during the pandemic, so I decided to follow my dream of becoming self sufficient one NFT at a time.
